{
  "$schema": "./control-inventory.schema.json",
  "version": 1,
  "notes": [
    "Source of truth for the per-control QA sweep.",
    "Each entry: id (DOM id), kind, optional collapsible (section ids whose inline display:none must be cleared before the control becomes reachable).",
    "Add new controls here, then run tests; drift guard will tell you if anything is missing or extra.",
    "Verify objects are intentionally minimal at v1 \u2014 they cover 'click does not throw' for most rows. Richer verify (network expectations, SSE assertions, forbiddenRequests, requiresState) is added incrementally as the sweep stabilises.",
    "data-testid='track-card' is scoped to descendants of #track-list ONLY (drag previews / modals MUST NOT carry it)."
  ],
